his is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://design-austin.com/ita/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 08:38:45','2016-08-02 08:38:45','',2,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(6,1,'2016-08-02 08:38:52','2016-08-02 08:38:52','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">PROPOSAL OF THE MONTH! 50% OFF FOR HAIR TECHNIQUE CLASS!</h3>\r\nWe are founded and led by Dr. Doran, who was trained as a doctor of Dermatology\r\nWe have built a reputation as one of the best vocational school in Illinois\r\nWe are an elite school, which has been called “Harvard of Skin care” by Spa owners\r\nWe offer the most advanced and updated Clinical Esthetics and Medical Assisting programs\r\nWe teach unique techniques and will make you the best in your profession\r\nWe believe that we can make the world a better place, by changing the lives of our students\r\nWe believe that professional development and education rises from a balance of support and challengeWe are a team fully invested in helping each student succeed in a new career\r\nWe take pride in the quality of education we provide for Skin Care, Medical Assisting, and Continuing Education!\r\nWe have developed high moral, ethical, and educational standards\r\nWe are committed to making our graduates the best they can be\r\nWe know that each student’s success is our success, and we share in their accomplishments\r\nWe have a 100% state licensure exam with one of the highest scores nationwide\r\nWe have a 100% graduation rate\r\nAll of our graduates are employed or self-employed\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The  philosophy  of  our  school  can  be  simply  described  by  three  inseparable  words: <strong>Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence!</strong></p>','Welcome','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2016-08-24 12:05:16','2016-08-24 12:05:16','',0,'http://design-austin.com/ita/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2016-08-02 08:38:52','2016-08-02 08:38:52','','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 08:38:52','2016-08-02 08:38:52','',6,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/6-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2016-08-24 12:05:05','2016-08-24 12:05:05','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">PROPOSAL OF THE MONTH! 50% OFF FOR HAIR TECHNIQUE CLASS!</h3>\nWe are founded and led by Dr. Doran, who was trained as a doctor of Dermatology\nWe have built a reputation as one of the best vocational school in Illinois\nWe are an elite school, which has been called “Harvard of Skin care” by Spa owners\nWe offer the most advanced and updated Clinical Esthetics and Medical Assisting programs\nWe teach unique techniques and will make you the best in your profession\nWe believe that we can make the world a better place, by changing the lives of our students\nWe believe that professional development and education rises from a balance of support and challengeWe are a team fully invested in helping each student succeed in a new career\nWe take pride in the quality of education we provide for Skin Care, Medical Assisting, and Continuing Education!\nWe have developed high moral, ethical, and educational standards\nWe are committed to making our graduates the best they can be\nWe know that each student’s success is our success, and we share in their accomplishments\nWe have a 100% state licensure exam with one of the highest scores nationwide\nWe have a 100% graduation rate\nAll of our graduates are employed or self-employed\n<p class=\"p1\">The philosophy of our school can be simply described by three inseparable words: <strong>Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence!</strong></p>','Welcome','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-autosave-v1','','','2016-08-24 12:05:05','2016-08-24 12:05:05','',6,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/6-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2016-08-02 08:39:58','2016-08-02 08:39:58','Everyone at our school has a passion for education. We believe that we can make the world a better place, by changing the lives of our students. We are a team, fully invested in helping each student succeed in a new career, finding happiness and balance in their lives. We take pride in the quality of education we provide for Skin Care, Medical Assisting, and Continuing Education!\r\n\r\nWe have developed high moral, ethical, and educational standards, and are committed to making our graduates the best they can be. Each student’s success is our success, and we share in their accomplishments. The philosophy of our school can be simply described by three inseparable words: Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence!','Welcome','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 08:39:58','2016-08-02 08:39:58','',6,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/6-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2016-08-02 08:54:04','2016-08-02 08:54:04','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2016-08-08 08:13:39','2016-08-08 08:13:39','',0,'http://design-austin.com/ita/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2016-08-02 08:54:04','2016-08-02 08:54:04','','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 08:54:04','2016-08-02 08:54:04','',10,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2016-08-02 08:54:12','2016-08-02 08:54:12','ContactContact ContactContact','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2016-08-02 08:54:12','2016-08-02 08:54:12','',10,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/02/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2016-08-02 10:26:21','2016-08-02 10:26:21','<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Values</h3>\r\nWe have developed the highest moral, ethical, and educational standards, and are committed to turning out the best professionals in the industry. Each student’s success is our success, and we share in their accomplishments. The philosophy of our school and be simply described by three inseparable words: Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence! \r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Quality</h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"> Quality is the fundamental core in every part of the education here at ITA. In the practice room and in the classroom, the quality of education is never compromised. We strive to bring in the new age of spa, salon, and healthcare techniques to raise the standards in the industry. Our unique curriculum stimulates our students to evolve into problem solvers. We focus on giving our students a complete understanding of all subject matters, not just memorizing correct answers. We know that a thorough understanding of any subject allows for logical decision making, which is critical for any working professional.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Professionalism</h3>\r\nWe prepare the most professional, confident, and successful Skin Care Therapists and Medical Assistants through our strong and well-structured education. Our graduates are universally successful! They take the best positions wherever they go, whether working with doctors, in salons, or in hospitals. Also, because of the confidence and self-esteem, which come with great level of knowledge and preparation, many of our graduates are self-employed and run successful businesses. \r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Excellence</h3>\r\nAt ITA, we have the strongest commitment to academic excellence, working hard to perfect our techniques, spending hundreds of hours doing “hands-on” practice.