 the highest scores nationwide\r\nWe have a 100% graduation rate\r\nAll of our graduates are employed or self-employed\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The  philosophy  of  our  school  can  be  simply  described  by  three  inseparable  words: <strong>Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence!</strong></p>','Welcome','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-revision-v1','','','2016-08-24 12:05:16','2016-08-24 12:05:16','',6,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/24/6-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(242,1,'2016-08-24 12:06:12','2016-08-24 12:06:12','<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Values</h3>\r\nWe have developed the highest moral, ethical, and educational standards, and are committed to turning out the best professionals in the industry. Each student’s success is our success, and we share in their accomplishments. The philosophy of our school and be simply described by three inseparable words: Quality, Professionalism, and Excellence!\r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Quality</h3>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Quality is the fundamental core in every part of the education at ITA.In the practice room and in the classroom, the quality of education is never compromised.  Our unique curriculum stimulates our students to evolve into problem solvers. We focus on giving our students a complete understanding of all the subject matters, not just memorizing correct answers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Professionalism</h3>\r\nWe prepare the most professional, confident, and successful Skin Care Therapists and Medical Assistants through our strong and well-structured education. Our graduates are universally successful! They take the best positions wherever they go, whether working with doctors, in salons, or in hospitals. Also, because of the confidence and self-esteem, which come with great level of knowledge and preparation, many of our graduates are self-employed and run successful businesses.\r\n<h3 class=\"cufon_headings\">Excellence</h3>\r\nAt ITA, we have the strongest commitment to academic