e bar in the fields of skin- and health care education\r\n• Help individuals train for fulfilling careers and obtain financial independence ','Excellence','We have a strong commitment to academic excellence, working hard  to  perfect  our  techniques,  spending  hundreds  of  hours  doing “hands-on”  practice.   Many salons owners request Academy’s graduates, some have called our school the “Harvard of Skin Care”.   Our   graduates   consistently   outperform   others   in   State   and   National   licenses   and certifications.','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2016-08-24 12:09:45','2016-08-24 12:09:45','',22,'http://design-austin.com/ita/2016/08/24/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(250,1,'2016-08-24 12:30:33','2016-08-24 12:30:33','We have trained hundreds of the best Skin- and Health Care professionals, who became universally successful – whether working in hospitals, with physicians, in salons, or being self-employed. So it is no wonder that our Academy is respected by business owners – and admired even by competitors - as the go-to place for exceptional, well-rounded hires. We have developed an Employer Network of top-notch medical offices, medispas, spas, and salons who happily employ our alumnae. Here are five reason\r\n\r\n1.Our graduates have unparalleled skills and training!\r\n2.Our graduates are incredibly driven and committed to being the best!\r\n3.Our graduates have tremendous work ethic!\r\n4.Our graduates have excellent communication skills and can handle even the most demanding clients/patients!\r\n5.Our graduates will be dedicated to making your business more successful and profitable!\r\n\r\nIf you would like to join our Employer Network and work with the Academy to get the best employees for your business, please fill out the form below:\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-8 col-md-offset-2\">[contact-form-7 id=\"254\" title=\"Recruit form\"]</div>','Recruit our Graduates','','publish','closed','closed','','recruit-our-graduates