sthetician!</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color:#ff0000;\"><span style=\"color:#000080;\"><strong>The October class is already full but <span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">REGISTER ONLINE</span></strong></span><span style=\"color:#000080;\"><strong>for November 17<sup>th</sup> class!</strong></span></span>\n<table style=\"height:181px;\" width=\"463\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\"><strong>Date</strong></td>\n<td width=\"68\"><strong>Day</strong></td>\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>Time</strong></td>\n<td width=\"63\"><strong>CEUs</strong></td>\n<td width=\"68\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">October 7 (Filled)</td>\n<td width=\"68\">Friday</td>\n<td width=\"126\">9:00a.m. - 1:30p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"63\">5 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"68\">$150.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"113\">November 17</td>\n<td width=\"68\">Monday</td>\n<td width=\"126\">5:00p.m. - 9:10p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"63\">5 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"68\">$150.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"color:#ff0000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000080;\">DON’T MISS OUT</span> on <span style=\"color:#000080;\">OTHER GREAT CLASSES <span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">in</span> OCTOBER</span>!</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><strong>Brazilian Done Easy &amp; Speedwaxing</strong></span>\n<table width=\"437\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"109\"><strong>Date</strong></td>\n<td width=\"72\"><strong>Day</strong></td>\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>Time</strong></td>\n<td width=\"63\"><strong>CEUs</strong></td>\n<td width=\"68\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"109\">October 13</td>\n<td width=\"72\">Monday</td>\n<td width=\"126\">9:00a.m. - 1:30p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"63\">5 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"68\">$150.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nWaxing procedures can make a huge part of the Esthetician income. Brazilian waxing is the fast growing and financially the most rewarding procedure. You do it right and fast the clients will never look for someone else. The class is designed to perfect you skills, share the tips helping you to improve your techniques, and find the way to increase your revenue.\n\n<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><strong>Advanced Chemical Peels for Skin Imperfections</strong></span>\n<table width=\"433\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"109\"><strong>Date</strong></td>\n<td width=\"72\"><strong>Day</strong></td>\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>Time</strong></td>\n<td width=\"63\"><strong>CEUs</strong></td>\n<td width=\"63\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"109\">October 25</td>\n<td width=\"72\">Saturday</td>\n<td width=\"126\">9:00a.m. - 1:30p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"63\">5 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"63\">$145.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nThe class will provide you extensive knowledge of a variety of topics, including medical classification of the skin, skin aging mechanisms, types of chemical peels, best techniques, contraindications, possible complications, the ways to avoid complications, the best ingredients to use with chemical peels and much more.\n\n<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><strong>Advanced Clinical/Paramedical Training (3 days)</strong></span>\n<table width=\"437\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"103\"><strong>Date</strong></td>\n<td width=\"78\"><strong>DAY</strong></td>\n<td width=\"126\"><strong>TIME</strong></td>\n<td width=\"68\"><strong>CEUs</strong></td>\n<td width=\"63\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"103\">October 11-13</td>\n<td width=\"78\">Sat.-Mon.</td>\n<td width=\"126\">9:00a.m. - 3:00p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"68\">20 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"63\">$695.00</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nThese three days will cover an enormous amount of information loading you with advanced knowledge on the latest concepts of Medical Esthetics.  It is a great blend of your current knowledge and new advanced procedures widely used in Medical setting. Among the topics covered are Medical Esthetics concepts, Recognition of skin conditions versus Skin disorders, Lymphatic system with Lymphatic massage, Dermaplanning, Aging Skin mechanisms, Best Antiaging Topicals, Skin Emergency situations, International Skin Classification and more.\n\n<span style=\"color:#339966;\"><strong>Laser Concepts: How far can you go? (Presented by AAMP)</strong></span>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"87\"><strong>Date</strong></td>\n<td width=\"74\"><strong>Day</strong></td>\n<td width=\"139\"><strong>Time</strong></td>\n<td width=\"75\"><strong>CEUs</strong></td>\n<td width=\"58\"><strong>Price</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"86\">October 18</td>\n<td width=\"74\"> Saturday</td>\n<td width=\"139\"> 9:00 a.m. - 6 p.m.</td>\n<td width=\"75\"> 10 CEUs</td>\n<td width=\"58\">$750</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nThe knowledge of the laser concepts is imperative. In order to deserve the trust of you client and show your professional knowledge, you need to understand what conditions can be treated with laser, what contraindications would be a red flag, and what complications can occur. Our clients ask our advice and opinion on the laser procedures all the time. Even Estheticians and Cosmetologists cannot operate Laser machines under their License, and the procedures have to be delegated by an MD. You will have hands-on training during the class.\n\n<span style=\"color:#ff0000;\"><strong>To register, go to <a href=\"http://www.isba.EventBrite.com\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;\">www.isba.EventBrite.com</span></a> or call us at 847-995-1932!</strong></span>\n\n&nbsp;','Micro-Needling CE Class','','publish','open','open','','micro-needling-ce-class','','','2014-09-16 09:10:30','2014-09-16 14:10:30','',0,'http://intlacademy.wordpress.com/?p=11418',0,'post','',0),(11442,2,'2014-10-15 07:37:02','2014-10-15 12:37:02','<span style=\"background-color:#eeeeee;\">We know that starting school is a big decision! To make it easier we are starting an evening Clinical Esthetics program on October 27!</span>\n\n<a href=\"http://design-austi